Class O2MCTest

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.o2mc.sdk.O2MCTest

  • public class O2MCTest
extends java.lang.Object
    This class checks if the O2MC class does not crash under any circumstance. Functionality of the methods is not verified here, but in the managers / util class(es).
